Name
       timing_report_constraint_enable_extended_drv_format

Syntax
       timing_report_constraint_enable_extended_drv_format

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables  the  software  to  report data as per clock/data and rise/fall
       phases.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

